				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Chu-qu%C3%A1-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-Lu%C3%A2n-thu%E1%BB%B7-ki%E1%BB%87t-v%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-ph%C3%A1t-nh%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-O71CAzygFNW4JNeF9p9JGA">Chu quá Đồng Luân thuỷ kiệt vị đắc phát nhân hứng - 舟過同倫水竭未得發因興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%C3%A1p-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BA%A5t-lang-nh%E1%BA%A5t-tuy%E1%BB%87t/poem-qv7wAk2cmctje35UNqE-ag">Đáp Trịnh thập thất lang nhất tuyệt - 答鄭十七郎一絕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-V%C4%83n-%C3%81i/H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-thi/poem-e60kDOCsbytSX90efY86Ag">Hương Sơn thi - 香山詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-V%C4%83n-%C3%81i/author-HFcTQNxpTDpHMR0gzqMkMg">Phan Văn Ái</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/Li%E1%BB%87t-n%E1%BB%AF-L%C3%BD-Tam-h%C3%A0nh/poem-kAXSQG8h5bUMBdRjj9Vfhg">Liệt nữ Lý Tam hành - 烈女李三行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/author-t5zNl0R6g-15oc9Dd33Eqg">Hồ Thiên Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BA%A1i-ng%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-thi%E1%BB%81n/poem-LvAgfE08bW_GHmspFhIapQ">Tại ngục vịnh thiền - 在獄詠蟬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-jvbfrjspi2Y6S8b3jeqzpA">Lạc Tân Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%E1%BB%87p-giang/poem-csh8ujkV1cSEGuoKbE1Ufg">Thiệp giang - 涉江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.